{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ac7dbafb16","title":"大字报诗——人之歌","origin":"《校内外右派言论汇集》(北京大学经济系政治经济学教研室，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ce4401900","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"ac7dbafb16"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c916c81c62","name":"张元勋"},{"id":"f66a6976b6","name":"沈泽宜"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"46b9f2f362","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——人之歌","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"3eadfa2c53","type":"authors","text":"北京大学沈泽宜张元勋","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"d2235ecb59","type":"subtitle","text":"（沈泽宜、张元勋：北京大学中文系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"1761f3a4d8","type":"paragraph","text":"应当学会尊重人——高尔基","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"9b3fb47986","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)序曲：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"7224dc46f5","type":"paragraph","text":"我们唱的不是颂歌，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"edc582495a","type":"paragraph","text":"也许有些人听来，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f7d8e1d7ee","type":"paragraph","text":"调子不太柔和","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4ae3e20a3c","type":"paragraph","text":"但，我们又大胆的高唱了：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"263811b449","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么还顾虑到会震破某些人的耳朵？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f03e41faa9","type":"paragraph","text":"摆开污蔑的中伤，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"cc5d2e7571","type":"paragraph","text":"我们又重新高唱，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"216bd4d5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"今天又伸出自由的手","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"476c52ec66","type":"paragraph","text":"把诗行贴到自由的墙上！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"9d67f14031","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)党员的特权","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"e2cae2eb5f","type":"paragraph","text":"——如果兄弟的心在哭泣，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"66a04e086c","type":"paragraph","text":"你怎能逼他唱快乐的歌?","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"1125d23934","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a37deac4de","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样的特权，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"065ee964c4","type":"paragraph","text":"长夜悠悠，大地黑暗迷漫，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"81506952d7","type":"paragraph","text":"你最先举起光明的火炬：","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"605bf5a208","type":"paragraph","text":"身上因而中了无数的枪弹。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"41712c3e59","type":"paragraph","text":"你是一个痛苦的纤夫，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"672ff447bb","type":"paragraph","text":"你衣衫褴褛。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"98b9c86e94","type":"paragraph","text":"火烫的阳光照跃当头","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a16a6e0f23","type":"paragraph","text":"脚下则是更烫的沙滩。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4337ed64a8","type":"paragraph","text":"你把一船受苦的人民","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"fae0564783","type":"paragraph","text":"投向新时代的岸边","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"b94355927b","type":"paragraph","text":"脚踝痛破了","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4cb8a86ff7","type":"paragraph","text":"一个脚印，一滩血水——","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"8afeea9111","type":"paragraph","text":"你坐在潮湿的监狱里。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"d81fbc58c5","type":"paragraph","text":"铁窗外白云舒卷；","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"0665df556c","type":"paragraph","text":"窗外有春日的阳光","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f9c3baced2","type":"paragraph","text":"树下的孩子一张瘦脸","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"168631e24c","type":"paragraph","text":"你爱这土地爱得更深","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"88af1cd94e","type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你痛苦的泪水清彻晶宝","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"fba55be69b","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到扼杀正义的断头台","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"589b363a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"你无畏地走上敌人的绞架。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"fd480af38a","type":"paragraph","text":"在那多雾的幽暗的残夜。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"6592a91a41","type":"paragraph","text":"你在慷慨悲歌中倒下。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"6cf3c24438","type":"paragraph","text":"你出没在烽火纵横的前线，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"78ae152452","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到反叛者的红旗下面","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"e09a08e40e","type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你振臂高呼","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"eec4cab157","type":"paragraph","text":"背后的群众似如潮涌；","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"88dd435dce","type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你跳进城墙的缺口","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a3d5f37898","type":"paragraph","text":"你最先爬上碉堡的墙垣；","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ba4409d0b7","type":"paragraph","text":"而当胜利的大旗","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"3a173ef34f","type":"paragraph","text":"终于在城头飘拂","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4b4cc15e54","type":"paragraph","text":"你却缓缓地顺着旗杆躺下。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"80c9f11212","type":"paragraph","text":"你眼含微笑","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"1a1e0a7354","type":"paragraph","text":"抬头仰望祖国的天空","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"5c2af09ba0","type":"paragraph","text":"黎明已呈现在东天","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"6a7e515ba2","type":"paragraph","text":"火红，火红……","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ec1af1351c","type":"paragraph","text":"大地苏醒，阳光灿烂。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"89ac7ae07a","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ad808d9dc8","type":"paragraph","text":"你有这样的特权","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"27db3d78e3","type":"paragraph","text":"你打扫城市的街道","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"20665c798c","type":"paragraph","text":"你点起工厂的炉灶","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"46fc62a81e","type":"paragraph","text":"从废墟和坟场上","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"26a17ed093","type":"paragraph","text":"修建起公园和学校。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f41d6ea833","type":"paragraph","text":"在早春的细雨里，","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"73729e8aa0","type":"paragraph","text":"你犁开江南的田亩","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"1ab14514e2","type":"paragraph","text":"走进烟熏的茅房，","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"c27c11c0a1","type":"paragraph","text":"喝一口家酿的酒浆；","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f261eaa8d4","type":"paragraph","text":"摸一摸磨光了的锄头柄","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"2d229426a9","type":"paragraph","text":"把它亲昵地放上肩膀。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"93ad7105af","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到旷无人烟的大漠，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"335c0f0efc","type":"paragraph","text":"古铜色的脸沐浴风尘；","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f8c4b63591","type":"paragraph","text":"你率领勘探队的勇士，","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"868b7a86ef","type":"paragraph","text":"朔风中回荡你的笑声。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ec0ca2e92b","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到怒江的河谷","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f62d151342","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到雪山的绝顶","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"264fd1a15b","type":"paragraph","text":"你手执蒙霜的步枪，","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"c10e6b7820","type":"paragraph","text":"巡逡在祖国的边境。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a2e39f6366","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到原始林区：","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"e7d3e7d88d","type":"paragraph","text":"风中的古木，雾里的泉声","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"1ee2fd4567","type":"paragraph","text":"你看惯了篝火与星月","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"66a592e4fa","type":"paragraph","text":"忙碌的采伐，雨雪的黄昏。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"da1bcca4d5","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到云雀高歌的北大荒","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"9eac6ec83f","type":"paragraph","text":"那儿曾是严寒统治的国度：","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"080a14e67a","type":"paragraph","text":"也许你被热病折磨得躺下","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"deafa0154a","type":"paragraph","text":"但，这是怎样的收成啊！","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a68cd25ed9","type":"paragraph","text":"金色的田野！金色的欢乐！","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"b84b3ccf1d","type":"paragraph","text":"你去到一切艰苦的地方，","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"f76b4faeff","type":"paragraph","text":"沿着河道，沿着山岗；","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"180f285572","type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿有你的歌声和脚迹！","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a797d7774b","type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿就出现城市和农庄。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ba735d8cef","type":"paragraph","text":"啊！共产党员！","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"6a1f5887c7","type":"paragraph","text":"这是你真正的特权","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"9ff242b482","type":"paragraph","text":"有谁使用得比你更好，","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"54885e0ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"有谁能把人民带到今天?","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"756c4c93e8","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，党啊！在你神圣的肌体内","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"37b13bedde","type":"paragraph","text":"却有这样的党员。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"29ee131205","type":"paragraph","text":"他们是你皮肤上的班毒疚，","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"538936076f","type":"paragraph","text":"他们醉心于另一种特权，","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"88619b6e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"对这样的人，我要大吼一声：","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"cc8fecf08e","type":"paragraph","text":"请听听一个公民的声音，","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"a2b8feb757","type":"paragraph","text":"请把眼光投向生活的深处","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"e47ec47db2","type":"paragraph","text":"投向人民音乐的底层!","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"e9711eb749","type":"paragraph","text":"在和平安逸的年代，","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"00acc0ca7e","type":"paragraph","text":"别忘了血泪洗刷的昨天，","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4fa43777ab","type":"paragraph","text":"不要侧着耳朵光听赞歌，","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"271d221627","type":"paragraph","text":"在喝乎声中，谄媚声里倦倦欲眠","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"50b7a4705c","type":"paragraph","text":"你那得意的，骄矜的笑，","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"5651011580","type":"paragraph","text":"只会使我双倍的辛酸。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"c3267b3583","type":"paragraph","text":"你一身“官气”越爬越高，","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ff3ecdef80","type":"paragraph","text":"离开群众路远迢迢，","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4195024cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，要小心哪！","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"9cbb0b5293","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一架雪作的梯子；","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4f273d865d","type":"paragraph","text":"经受不住太阳的照跃！","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"023d0e7a78","type":"paragraph","text":"不要贪图地位和金钱，","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"86a5621338","type":"paragraph","text":"回忆一下悲惨的童年，","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"5d9a8b566a","type":"paragraph","text":"回忆一下故乡的房舍，","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"20a3519669","type":"paragraph","text":"多少人家断了炊烟；","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"5dea364d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"不要光想娇妻爱子，","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"cdd52f3b62","type":"paragraph","text":"多多想想烈士的寡妻","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"eff01cb65b","type":"paragraph","text":"还是有不少寒贫的老者","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ad3f9b5fb0","type":"paragraph","text":"还有不少失学的孩子。","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"4bd8b88f74","type":"paragraph","text":"不许凌辱纯洁的少女","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"af1b4d5ab8","type":"paragraph","text":"姿意滥用恶心的权势，","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"3d601f9e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"不许伸出欲念的长舌，","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"650c418212","type":"paragraph","text":"对着鲜花垂涎欲滴，","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"ae03958a71","type":"paragraph","text":"不许对教授乱打官腔，","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac7dbafb16"},{"id":"34f62354c3","type":"paragraph","text":"你还没